product_name: Bison Designs Clip Art Carabiner Keychain
long_description: A stylish and unique way to manage your keys! These painted carabiners have different themes to suit your mood. Painted aluminum carabiner is lightweight and comes with split ring for key attachment. Clipit(TM) carabiner clips to keys, purses, backpacks, cell phones and sports equipment. Not intended for climbing or load-bearing use.
